The 2022 Honda CR-V Sport is a compact SUV known for its reliability, practicality, and modern features. Below are the key details about this model:

Engine and Performance:
Engine: 1.5-liter turbocharged inline-4
Horsepower: 190 hp
Torque: 179 lb-ft
Transmission: Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) with Sport Mode
Fuel Efficiency: Approximately 28 mpg city / 34 mpg highway (FWD)
Drive Type: Front-wheel drive (FWD) or optional all-wheel drive (AWD)
Dimensions:
Overall Length: 182.1 inches
Width: 73.0 inches
Height: 66.5 inches
Wheelbase: 104.7 inches
Curb Weight: Around 3,337 lbs (FWD)
Interior Features:
Seating Capacity: 5
Upholstery: Cloth or optional leather
Infotainment System: 7-inch touchscreen display with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
Audio System: 6-speaker audio system
Connectivity: Bluetooth hands-free link, USB ports
Comfort: Dual-zone automatic climate control, 8-way power-adjustable driver's seat
Safety and Driver Assistance:
Airbags: Front, side, and curtain airbags
Braking System: Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) with Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD)
Stability Control: Vehicle Stability Assist (VSA) with Traction Control
Advanced Safety Features: Honda Sensing suite, including Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS), Road Departure Mitigation System (RDM), Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow, Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS), Forward Collision Warning (FCW), and Lane Departure Warning (LDW)
Exterior:
Wheels: 18-inch alloy wheels
Lighting: LED headlights, LED fog lights, LED daytime running lights
Mirrors: Power-adjustable, heated side mirrors with integrated turn signals
Sunroof: Optional power moonroof
Additional Features:
Convenience: Smart Entry with Walk Away Auto Lock, Remote Engine Start
Storage: 39.2 cubic feet of cargo space behind the rear seats, expanding to 75.8 cubic feet with rear seats folded
Other Features: Roof rails, rear privacy glass
Additional Notes:
The 2022 Honda CR-V Sport offers a balanced mix of performance, comfort, and advanced safety features, making it a strong contender in the compact SUV segment. It is designed to meet the needs of families and individuals looking for a versatile and reliable vehicle.

If you have any specific questions or need more detailed information about this model, feel free to ask! "}]

description: [{'description': "Experience the 2019 Honda CR-V LX, a versatile and dependable SUV now available at Bruce Honda in Yarmouth, NS. Known for its blend of practicality, comfort, and advanced features, the CR-V LX is an excellent choice for families, commuters, and adventurers alike.The exterior of the 2019 CR-V LX showcases a modern and sleek design, characterized by bold lines, a distinctive front grille, and stylish 17-inch alloy wheels. Its refined appearance is further enhanced by LED daytime running lights and a rear spoiler, adding both functionality and aesthetic appeal.Under the hood, the 2019 CR-V LX is powered by a 2.4-liter 4-cylinder engine, delivering 184 horsepower and a smooth driving experience. Paired with a continuously variable transmission (CVT), this powertrain offers excellent fuel economy and responsive handling, making it perfect for both city commutes and long road trips.Inside the spacious cabin, the 2019 CR-V LX offers a comfortable and well-appointed interior with high-quality materials and advanced features. The interior includes supportive cloth seats, a 5-inch color LCD screen, Bluetooth connectivity, and a rearview camera. The CR-V LX also provides ample cargo space with easy-folding rear seats to accommodate all your gear, whether you're heading to the grocery store or on a weekend getaway.Safety is a top priority in the 2019 CR-V LX, which comes equipped with a suite of advanced safety and driver-assist features. Standard features include the Honda Sensing technologies, which offer adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, collision mitigation braking, and road departure mitigation. These features ensure peace of mind for you and your passengers on every journey.Bruce Honda, located at 166 Starrs Rd in Yarmouth, NS, invites you to explore the 2019 Honda CR-V LX. With a commitment to customer satisfaction and a reputation for excellence, Bruce Honda is your trusted destination for this reliable and stylish SUV. "}]

description:
[{'description': "
The 2021 Honda CR-V Sport is a well-equipped trim level within the CR-V lineup, offering a balance of features, performance, and value. Here are some key features you can expect in the 2021 Honda CR-V Sport:
	
	
Engine: It is equipped with a 1.5-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder engine, which provides a good balance of power and fuel efficiency. This engine is known for its smooth performance and responsive acceleration.
	
	
	
Transmission: Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT), which is known across most Honda models for its efficiency and smooth operation.
	
	
	
Interior Comfort: The CR-V Sport includes cloth upholstery with sporty trim accents. It has heated front seats, a driver's seat with power adjustments, and ample cargo space thanks to the CR-V's versatile layout.
	
	
	
Infotainment: It comes with a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allowing seamless smartphone connectivity for navigation, music, and hands-free calls.
	
	
	
Exterior Styling: The CR-V Sport may feature 18-inch alloy wheels, fog lights, and sporty exterior accents such as a gloss-black grille and body-colored door handles and mirrors.
	
	
	
Optional Features: Depending on the market and specific configuration, optional features might include a premium audio system, a panoramic sunroof, and leather-trimmed seats.
	

Overall, the 2021 Honda CR-V Sport is designed for drivers seeking a blend of practicality, comfort, and modern technology in a compact SUV package. It's a popular choice among families and commuters alike due to its reliability, versatility, and extensive feature set
As a Steele Auto Certified vehicle, you have peace of mind that the vehicle has undergone a rigorous 85 point inspection and has been brought up to the highest of standards. Don't forget, at Steele Volkswagen we have financing options available for all credit situations! "}]

description: [{'description': 'Discover the 2023 Honda CR-V Sport, a versatile and stylish SUV now available at Bruce Honda in Yarmouth, NS. The CR-V Sport is designed to offer a perfect balance of performance, comfort, and advanced features, making it an excellent choice for families, commuters, and adventurers alike.The exterior of the 2023 CR-V Sport boasts a sleek and modern design, characterized by bold lines, a distinctive front grille, and sporty 19-inch alloy wheels. Its refined appearance is further enhanced by LED headlights, taillights, and fog lights, ensuring you make a statement wherever you go.Under the hood, the 2023 CR-V Sport is powered by a responsive 1.5-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder engine, delivering 190 horsepower and a smooth driving experience. Paired with a continuously variable transmission (CVT), this powertrain provides excellent fuel efficiency and responsive handling, making it ideal for both city driving and long road trips.Inside the spacious and well-designed cabin, the 2023 CR-V Sport offers a comfortable and practical environment with high-quality materials and advanced features. The interior includes supportive cloth seats, a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and Bluetooth connectivity. Additional features such as a multi-angle rearview camera, keyless entry, and push-button start add to the convenience and enjoyment of every drive.Safety is a top priority in the 2023 CR-V Sport, which comes equipped with Honda Sensing technologies. This suite of advanced safety and driver-assist features includes adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, collision mitigation braking, and road departure mitigation, providing peace of mind for you and your passengers on every journey.Bruce Honda, located at 166 Starrs Rd in Yarmouth, NS, invites you to explore the 2023 Honda CR-V Sport.
